@Barry Ancona as I suspected. I just looked at my times going back to April. My average Thurs time is 19:03. Going backward, this one was 8:49, then 8:29 last week, then 8:53, 8:27, 10:37, 7:49, 10:02, then on April 23 17:38. That is, I have to go back 8 puzzles to find a time that approaches my average solve time. And in Aprul the rest were all still below that 17:38 time, with a particular nadir on 9 April, which I solved in 6:35.

I try not talk about solve times on here unless I hit some incredible PB on a Monday or something, because I’m genuinely not speed-solving Thursdays. But for me it’s no joke; Thursday has been a massive disappointment for several weeks, and I can see that disappointment reflected in the data.

